# PWA & project structure

Full checklist: `docs/static-site-standards.md` (PWA, File structure, Validation, Version control, Misc).

## Root / deploy files

- `404.html`, `robots.txt`, `sitemap.xml`, optional `humans.txt`
- Favicons: `favicon.ico`, `favicon.svg`, `apple-touch-icon`
- `.well-known/security.txt`, `CNAME`, `.nojekyll` (GitHub Pages)
- Target dirs: `/assets/`, `/images/`, `/css/`, `/js/`; `index.html` per route folder

## PWA (optional — implement when requested)

- `manifest.json` (maskable icons), `sw.js` (Cache API + offline fallback)
- `theme-color` meta, install prompt UX, `apple-touch-icon`

## Validation before release

- W3C HTML/CSS validators, Lighthouse, PageSpeed Insights, WebPageTest
- securityheaders.com, SSL Labs, Mozilla Observatory
- Rich Results + Schema validators; OG debuggers; link checker (Lychee)

## Git

- Conventional commits; branches `main` / `dev`; tags for releases
